dcterms:description: A relatively small dataset that consists of 50,000 training images with 500 images per class, and 10,000 testing images with 100 images per class. The images in CIFAR100 are RGB with a size of 32 × 32 pixels.
dcterms:title: CIFAR100

dcterms:description: A subset of 100 classes randomly selected from ImageNet, which consists of 129,395 training images and 5,000 testing images. The images in ImageNet100 are RGB with a size of 224 × 224 pixels.
dcterms:title: ImageNet100

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 100,000 training images with 500 images per class, and 10,000 testing images with 50 images per class. All images in TinyImageNet are downsampled to 64 × 64.
dcterms:title: TinyImageNet
